name: "Are You Dead Inside?" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing created in MS Paint.] This is an old piece, created in April of 2013 for my blog at that time, The Primitive Entertainment Workshop. This image has never been released as an NFT...until NOW! (Be careful, though. I think this piece MIGHT be cursed...) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
